{"tid":1052000,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"投資同賭博，有咩唔同？","createTime":"2019-03-08T04:18:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T08:26:32.000Z","uid":123335,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cbcafb91afd9369b432fd66531d5ced17f908bff","tid":1052000,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:18:54.000Z","msg":"賭博都有得分析 <br />\nEg 賭馬<br />\n注碼控制、statistics、基本面分析、投注額既流動 .... etc <br />\n<br />\n玩到咁pro <br />\n好似果個中大教授寫program賭馬贏左幾千萬 <br />\n咁仲算唔算賭博？<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，<br />\n我睇財經新聞，睇某隻股票既業績，睇年報 <br />\n去買入覺得有潛力既股票<br />\n點知輸左20% 忍痛止蝕 <br />\n咁我算唔算投資？"},{"pid":"16d3051bb47b9d9fa97d91063fff3ff185361fc4","tid":1052000,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"投資有得坐"},{"pid":"316c1362c3a460e6df6ace89833229405c98d08d","tid":1052000,"uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"16d3051bb47b9d9fa97d91063fff3ff185361fc4","tid":1052000,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"投資有得坐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"坐到d 貨蟹晒<br />\n仲算唔算投資？"},{"pid":"cc7d998c8895bb4d6751396b1b5b9f2c63e42f56","tid":1052000,"uid":131298,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"316c1362c3a460e6df6ace89833229405c98d08d","tid":1052000,"uid":123335,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"16d3051bb47b9d9fa97d91063fff3ff185361fc4","tid":1052000,"uid":2140,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:19:41.000Z","msg":"投資有得坐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:20:19.000Z","msg":"坐到d 貨蟹晒<br />\n仲算唔算投資？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:26:43.000Z","msg":"計到數返到本就算"},{"pid":"d0e010b126f5e51cf5b7efb860af4ed753734ad0","tid":1052000,"uid":123335,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:26:50.000Z","msg":"呢個問題我諗左好耐都諗唔明<br />\n<br />\n又舉個例 <br />\n當年次按危機，就係投資公司<br />\n用「投資」手法，借錢俾班低信用評級既人買樓 <br />\n點知搞出左金融危機，好多大型投資銀行倒閉<br />\nEg 雷曼 <br />\n<br />\n咁佢地當年推出次按，<br />\n係投資？ 定賭博？"},{"pid":"11e928213f80b3ef23de3a321ff9e9c6c9ffe1e0","tid":1052000,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"冇咩唔同<br />\n不過賭博有兩種<br />\n馬足呢類操控性過多<br />\n同投資一樣人為多<br />\n賭大細 純運氣<br />\n又唔同"},{"pid":"4e5ff6b23745b826d6644d989d3ba1a1270f2152","tid":1052000,"uid":240654,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:29:20.000Z","msg":"你贏左咪叫投資有道<br />\n輸咪叫投機同賭博"},{"pid":"2be5d47b3e8726745442d6e6ad8dd329a972056e","tid":1052000,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"買左邊隻先？<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔啱價入都係輸。<br />\n就好似150買舜宇肯定仆街啦。"},{"pid":"03716ea62e7b7868090205daa336517149df438c","tid":1052000,"uid":94338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2be5d47b3e8726745442d6e6ad8dd329a972056e","tid":1052000,"uid":169071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:36:15.000Z","msg":"買左邊隻先？<br />\n<br />\n就算你唔啱價入都係輸。<br />\n就好似150買舜宇肯定仆街啦。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:40:34.000Z","msg":"坐二年升返151咪賺1蚊囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f37715d0496f44690a1d21dc7d302e69577fff24","tid":1052000,"uid":79481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:42:48.000Z","msg":"賭搏通常ev係細過0<br />\n<br />\n好似賭大細咁 就算最fair既21點都係細過0<br />\n<br />\n投資ev可以大過0<br />\n<br />\n長玩既話係可以賺<br />\n<br />\n如果你講賭波賭馬分析<br />\n<br />\n你真係量化到所有野 令到你ev大過0<br />\n<br />\n咁咪係投資而唔係賭"},{"pid":"1c40785fd960319a25c73fd54e9adf928149ec9c","tid":1052000,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11e928213f80b3ef23de3a321ff9e9c6c9ffe1e0","tid":1052000,"uid":25108,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:28:58.000Z","msg":"冇咩唔同<br />\n不過賭博有兩種<br />\n馬足呢類操控性過多<br />\n同投資一樣人為多<br />\n賭大細 純運氣<br />\n又唔同"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T04:44:39.000Z","msg":"去賭場賭大細 <br />\n呢d 就真係純賭博，純運氣 <b